<sect1 role="feedback">
  <title>Feedback</title>
  <para>Do you have <emphasis role="bold">comments</emphasis> on any of the things <emphasis
      role="bold">mentioned</emphasis> in this article? Then head right over to the <ulink
        url="http://bit.ly/kH55SM"
      >comment section</ulink> and let us know! </para>
  <para>Or if you would like to be <emphasis role="bold">part</emphasis> of the <ulink
      url="http://en.opensuse.org/openSUSE:Weekly_news_team">openSUSE:Weekly news team</ulink> then
    check out our team page and join! </para>
  <para>If you don't know, how to <emphasis role="bold">contribute</emphasis>, just check out the
      <ulink url="http://en.opensuse.org/openSUSE:Weekly_news_contribute">Contribution
    Page</ulink>.</para>
  <para>We have a <ulink url="http://os-news.ietherpad.com/2">Etherpad</ulink>, which you can also
    use to sumbit news.</para>
  <para><emphasis role="bold">Talk with us:</emphasis></para>
  <para>Or <emphasis role="bold">Communicate</emphasis> with or get help from the wider openSUSE
    community via IRC, forums, or mailing lists see <ulink
      url="http://en.opensuse.org/openSUSE:Communication_channels">Communicate</ulink>. </para>
  <para>Visit our <emphasis role="bold">connect.opensuse.org</emphasis> Page: <ulink
      url="https://connect.opensuse.org/pg/groups/10679/weekly-news-team/">and give your
      Feedback.</ulink></para>
  <para>Visit our <emphasis role="bold">Facebook</emphasis> Fanpage: <ulink
      url="http://www.facebook.com/pages/OpenSUSE-Weekly-News/164052946964277"
    >Fanpage</ulink></para>
  <para>You also can submit via <ulink
      url="http://developer.berlios.de/bugs/?group_id=12095">Bugtracking</ulink> and <ulink
      url="http://developer.berlios.de/feature/?group_id=12095">Featurerequests</ulink> for give
    your Feedback.</para>
  <para><emphasis role="bold">Keep updated:</emphasis></para>
  <para>You can subscribe to the openSUSE Weekly News <emphasis role="bold">RSS</emphasis> feed at
      <ulink url="http://news.opensuse.org/category/weekly-news/feed/"
    >news.opensuse.org</ulink>.</para>
  <para><emphasis role="bold">DOCS</emphasis>: Visit the official openSUSE docs page: <ulink
      url="http://doc.opensuse.org">docs.opensuse.org</ulink>.</para>
  <para>Wish to <emphasis role="bold">donate</emphasis>? <ulink
      url="http://flattr.com/thing/135641/openSUSE-Weekly-News">
      <inlinemediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="http://api.flattr.com/button/flattr-badge-large.png"/>
        </imageobject>
      </inlinemediaobject></ulink>
  </para>
</sect1>
